#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.negative\\_binomial"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a negative binomial distribution."
msgstr "从负二项分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a negative binomial distribution with specified "
"parameters, `n` trials and `p` probability of success where `n` is an "
"integer > 0 and `p` is in the interval [0, 1]."
msgstr ""
"样本是从具有指定参数的负二项分布中抽取的，`n` 次试验和成功的概率 `p`，"
"其中 `n` 是一个大于 0 的整数，`p` 在区间 [0, 1] 内。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:7 of
msgid ""
"Parameter of the distribution, > 0. Floats are also accepted, but they "
"will be truncated to integers."
msgstr "分布的参数，> 0。浮点数也可以接受，但会被截断为整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:10 of
msgid "Parameter of the distribution, >= 0 and <=1."
msgstr "分布的参数，>= 0 且 <=1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:12 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``n`` and ``p`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``np.broadcast(n, p).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 是 ``None``（默认），并且 ``n`` 和 ``p`` 都是标量，则返回"
"单个值。否则，抽取 ``np.broadcast(n, p).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:17 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:19 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:21 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:24 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized negative binomial "
"distribution, where each sample is equal to N, the number of trials it "
"took to achieve n - 1 successes, N - (n - 1) failures, and a success on "
"the, (N + n)th trial."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 从参数化的负二项分布中抽取的样本，其中每个样本等于 N，即达到 n"
" - 1 次成功所需的试验次数，N - (n - 1) 次失败，以及在第 (N + n) 次试验中"
"成功。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:31 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:32 of
msgid "The probability density for the negative binomial distribution is"
msgstr "负二项分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:34 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"P(N;n,p) = \\binom{N+n-1}{n-1}p^{n}(1-p)^{N},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:36 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`n-1` is the number of successes, :math:`p` is the "
"probability of success, and :math:`N+n-1` is the number of trials. The "
"negative binomial distribution gives the probability of n-1 successes and"
" N failures in N+n-1 trials, and success on the (N+n)th trial."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`n-1` 是成功的次数，:math:`p` 是成功的概率，:math:`N+n-1` 是"
"试验的次数。负二项分布给出了在 N+n-1 次试验中 n-1 次成功和 N 次失败的概率"
"，以及在第 (N+n) 次试验中成功。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:42 of
msgid ""
"If one throws a die repeatedly until the third time a \"1\" appears, then"
" the probability distribution of the number of non-\"1\"s that appear "
"before the third \"1\" is a negative binomial distribution."
msgstr ""
"如果一个人反复掷骰子，直到第三次出现 \"1\"，那么在第三次出现 \"1\" 之前"
"出现的非 \"1\" 的数量的概率分布就是负二项分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:47 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:48 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Negative Binomial Distribution.\" From MathWorld--A "
"Wolfram Web Resource. "
"http://mathworld.wolfram.com/NegativeBinomialDistribution.html"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:51 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Negative binomial distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Negative_binomial_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:55 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:56 of
msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.negative_binomial.negative_binomial:58 of
msgid ""
"A real world example. A company drills wild-cat oil exploration wells, "
"each with an estimated probability of success of 0.1.  What is the "
"probability of having one success for each successive well, that is what "
"is the probability of a single success after drilling 5 wells, after 6 "
"wells, etc.?"
msgstr ""
"一个现实世界的例子。一家公司钻探野猫油井，每口井的成功概率估计为 0.1。"
"每口连续的井有一次成功的概率是多少，也就是说，钻探 5 口井后有一次成功的"
"概率是多少，钻探 6 口井后有一次成功的概率是多少，等等。"

